      "id": "bug-028",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-12T00:00:00.000Z",
      "error_message": "Alumni email not in registry shows student-centric error: 'Only TU/e institutional email addresses are accepted'",
      "file": "apps/server/src/index.ts",
      "root_cause": "isAllowedEnrolmentEmail() combined student+alumni validation into one boolean, so both rejection cases returned TUE_DOMAIN_ERROR regardless of whether the email was a failed alumni lookup. ALUMNI_REGISTRY_ERROR and ALUMNI_REGISTRY_UNAVAILABLE_ERROR constants existed but were unused.",
      "fix": "Split handleSendOtp into explicit branches: TU/e domain → proceed; non-TU/e + in alumni registry → proceed; non-TU/e + not in registry → ALUMNI_REGISTRY_ERROR (400); registry throws → ALUMNI_REGISTRY_UNAVAILABLE_ERROR (503). Removed isAllowedEnrolmentEmail helper.",
      "tags": [
        "auth",
        "alumni",
        "error-message",
        "verification",
        "hono"
      ],
      "related_bugs": ["bug-006", "bug-007", "bug-015"],
      "occurrences": 1,
